ğŸ° Simple Slot Machine Game (Python)

This project is a fun and interactive slot machine simulator written in Python.
The player starts with a balance of $100 and can place bets to spin the slot machine. If all 3 symbols match, the player wins a payout based on the symbol type!

This program demonstrates:

Random selection

Lists and loops

Input validation

Simple reward logic

Basic game flow

