ğŸ§  How the Game Works

Player enters a bet

Program deducts the bet from balance

Slot machine spins and displays 3 symbols

Payout is calculated with get_payout()

Balance is updated

Game continues until balance reaches $0

ğŸ›  Requirements

Python 3.x

Uses only built-in modules (random, time)

